          <p class='first-para'>
            First, I congratulate the hon. Member for Orkney and Shetland (Mr. Carmichael) on securing the debate. I regret the fact that the House authorities did not find it possible to have the sitting of the Constitutional Affairs Committee at a time that did not coincide with this debate in Westminster Hall.
